summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to zoning and land use; adding Chapter 23.80 to Title 23 of the Seattle Municipal Code to provide criteria and a process for developing and considering Master Plans for major institutions; and adding Chapter 23.82 and amending Sections 23.76.50, 23.76.54, 23.76.56, 23.76.62, and 23.76.64 to Title 23 of the Seattle Municipal Code to provide criteria and a process for designating new Major Institutions.
